title: The Junction House - Cafe & Restaurant Seminyak
address: In front of Seminyak Square, Kayu Aya No.3 Seminyak Kerobokan Kelod Kuta Utara, Seminyak, Kec. Kuta, Kabupaten Badung, Bali 80361
street: In front of Seminyak Square, Kayu Aya No.3 Seminyak Kerobokan Kelod Kuta Utara
note_from_owner:
The Junction House establishment is inspired by urban-styled Haussmann Parisian House, the classic French building style. Located perfectly on Seminyak busy junction, it’s a perfect place to kick off the day with a cup of best coffee and hearty breakfast, relax and recharge during the day or gather with friends and families for dinner.

ALL DAY DINING
Hungry? Pop in for your catch-up sessions with besties or lunch with family, even dinner with loved one. Worry not, our all day dining menu supports you all the way!

We aim to make you feel the most at home, except in a Parisian apartment located in Bali.

title: D'Crepes Level 21
address: DENPASAR JUNCTION, Jl. Teuku Umar No.1, Dauh Puri Klod, Kec. Denpasar Bar., Kota Denpasar, Bali 80113
street: DENPASAR JUNCTION, Jl. Teuku Umar No.1
note_from_owner:
Dcrepes adalah pelopor pertama produk crepes di Indonesia. Berdiri dibawah naungan PT. Jaddi Pastrisindo Gemilang pada tahun 1996 dengan lokasi pertama di Plaza Senayan, Jakarta. Dcrepes menyajikan beragam menu lezat yang disuka berbagi kalangan, mulai dari anak-anak sampai dewasa dengan harga yang terjangkau.

Dcrepes memiliki 3 varian menu andalan, yaitu Sweet Crepes seperti Nutella Cheese, Silverqueen dan Banana Choco Cheese. Savory Crepes dengan pilihan isian daging lezat seperti Chili Dog, Smoked Beef & Cheese dan Beef Yakiniku. Selain itu ada Ice Cream Crepes untuk para penggemar cold dessert dengan menu Strawberry Special dan Choco Lovers. Ketiga varian ini hadir dalam 3 tipe kulit crepes, Crispy, Savory dan Soft Crepes.
